Number":16,"content":"  A2 validatePackage：按「包内被引用 agentId」校验；PARTICIPANT_* 降级","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":17,"content":"  A3 磁盘包迁移 + 需求 01/08 口径更新","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":18,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":19,"content":"阶段 B · 包内卡生命周期（P0）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":41,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":42,"content":"阶段 G · UX 债 + 校验定位 + 收口","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":43,"content":"  G1 删遗留角色 + golden_handoff/demo-user 迁移；变体 id；时段 Select；包列表搜索+新建","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":44,"content":"  G2 保存前 validatePackage + error 路径定位（package/card/exit）；阻断写盘","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":45,"content":"  G3 docs/AI 同步 + 全批验收勾选","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":46,"content":"```","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":47,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":51,"content":"|------|------|","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":52,"content":"| Host / beginCall / Effect **真执行** | 编辑器仍只写 Content；不 pretend 调试闭环 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":53,"content":"| 通话中 RuntimeExitCandidate / 工具运行时 UI | 动态出口 `exitKind: dynamic` 仍禁止内容 JSON 手写 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":54,"content":"| 调试器 **真会话**（beginCall 驱动） | 可选尾任务仅读盘展示 validate，不 Host |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":55,"content":"| 导入导出正式 ZIP 管道 | 列表导入保持现状 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":56,"content":"| 第二幕内容包 | 不扩叙事 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":57,"content":"| 单卡增量 API | 仍整包保存 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":66,"content":"| 细化修改 7 | Effect 15 种面板已通；本批补 critical roundtrip、资产 id 真源 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":67,"content":"| docs/AI 07 | 资源库/条件 DSL/新建包等纳入本批 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":68,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":69,"content":"**刀序铁律：** A → B → C → D → E → F → G。**禁止**跳步（例：未改 validate 就先全库锚点双轨；未 E1 就宣称 ASSET 校验可编）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":70,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":71,"content":"### 1.4 本批完成后仍有意未覆盖（勿误判为 bug）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":72,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":73,"content":"| 项 | 说明 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":74,"content":"|----|------|","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":75,"content":"| Host 跑通第一幕 | 需另里程碑 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":76,"content":"| 调试器逐步调试 / Outcome 构造闭环 | 可选 S8-19 仅 validate 展示 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":77,"content":"| 工具 inputSchema 表单化 | Registry 只读下拉即可 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":78,"content":"| revealPolicy 等 context 稀有字段 | 无 UI 时仍可直接改 JSON |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":79,"content":"| 导入导出 / 壳嵌入打包 | 另批 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":94,"content":"| participants | 新包可不写；保存推荐不写；校验现场派生 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":95,"content":"| layout.lanes | Studio 按库序或「有卡者优先」派生；引擎忽略 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":96,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":97,"content":"### 2.1 引擎 validatePackage 改造","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":98,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":99,"content":"1. **`collectReferencedAgentIds(bundle)`**：扫描 ownerAgentId、effects.agentId、end_story.next.agentId、attach 目标归属等（与 validate 一致）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":100,"content":"2. **`REFERENCED_AGENT_UNKNOWN`**（error）：派生 id 不在角色库。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":101,"content":"3. **`validateParticipantsCharacters`** 对**派生集合**执行。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":102,"content":"4. **`PARTICIPANT_UNKNOWN`**：非空遗留 participants 未知 → **warning**「遗留字段将忽略」；空数组不报错。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":103,"content":"5. **ownerAgentId 不在旧 participants** 但在角色库 → 不得 error。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":104,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":109,"content":"| 底栏放置新 CallCard | 生成 cardId；追加 `conf.cards[]`；新建 `cards/<cardId>.s-card.json`；画布节点与 conf 一致 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":110,"content":"| 画布删除 CallCard | 从 `conf.cards[]` 移除；**删除**对应 s-card 文件（若 entryCardId 指向该卡则阻止或强制改入口） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":111,"content":"| 保存整包 | `editorGraphToBundle` 写回 **conf.cards 与磁盘卡文件并集**（以画布为准），禁止只改 layout 不改 conf |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":112,"content":"| orphan 磁盘卡 | 未在 conf 索引的 s-card → validate `CARD_FILE_ORPHAN` warning；保存时可清理或保留策略写清 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":113,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":114,"content":"**禁止：** 仅会话内新增节点，保存后 conf 仍只有打开时的卡列表。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":115,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":154,"content":"| API | `/api/assets` 列表/读/写/删；Studio 资源库页与 AssetPickerFloat 读 API |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":155,"content":"| 删除 mock | 接通后删 `MOCK_ASSETS` / `listMockAssets` 作业务真源（零残余） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":156,"content":"| 引用 | `playbackClipId`、`play_system_prompt.clipId` 下拉来自 API；`conf.assetRefs` 可编辑（多选或列表） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":157,"content":"| validate | 保存 validate 时 `ASSET_UNKNOWN` / `ASSET_URI_MISSING` 可真实拦错 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":158,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":159,"content":"头像：`POST /api/characters/:id/avatar` 或复用 assets 管道；**去掉** assetId 手填主路径。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":160,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":171,"content":"| 项 | 口径 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":172,"content":"|----|------|","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":173,"content":"| 搜索 | filter title / packageId |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":174,"content":"| 新建 | `POST /api/stories` 最小 conf（可无 participants）+ layout + 可选默认 entry 卡 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":175,"content":"| 删除 mock | `commitCreatePackageMock` throw 清零 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":176,"content":"| characterCount | 派生「本包引用角色数」 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":177,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":181,"content":"- **C2** 变体 id UUID 自动生成，UI 隐藏。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":182,"content":"- **C3** LocalHourRangeField → 双 Select。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":183,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":184,"content":"### 2.10 保存 validate + 定位","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":185,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":186,"content":"| 项 | 口径 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":187,"content":"|----|----