ath / message`；可解析 `cards/<cardId>.s-card.json#exits.<exitId>…` → `selectCallCardByCardId` 选中画布卡并开属性浮窗。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":72,"content":"- **默认包：** 路由 `wrong_number_act1`；缺 layout 时 BFF 安全默认坐标。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true}]},{"file":"docs/AI/studio-v2/07-已知边界与下一步候选.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":1,"content":"# 已知边界与下一步候选（代码事实）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":2,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":3,"content":"> 固化：2026-07-23（V2-S8-18：保存 validate 闸门 + card 级错误定位）。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":4,"content":"> 「站稳」指：角色/玩家/故事包列表/编辑器读写+编辑接线+保存校验均可磁盘真源；**不等于** Host 闭环。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":5,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":12,"content":"| 故事包 BFF + UI | **已做**：列表扫盘；编辑器打开/整包保存；`CanvasMockGraph` 已删 | 勿再写「打开仍走内存种子」 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":13,"content":"| 编辑接线落盘 | **已做**：浮窗/出口/Effect/归属经整包保存写 cards+layout | 不等于 Host 真跑 Effect |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":14,"content":"| 保存 validate | **已做**：PUT 写后 `validatePackage`；error 回滚阻断；条幅定位到 card | warning 默认不阻断；exit 级仅 path 展示 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":15,"content":"| 资源库落盘 | **已做**：`data/assets` ↔ `/api/assets`（细化修改 8） | 勿再写 MOCK_ASSETS 业务真源 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":16,"content":"| Host 跑通第一幕 | 无 | 出口/Effect 仍是编辑器写 Content |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":17,"content":"| 调试器真会话 | 仍 mock / 可选 S8-19 仅读盘展示 validate | 本步不 Host beginCall |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":18,"content":"| 正式稿逐句剧本 | speakable 压缩 | 不是完整剧本导入器 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":19,"content":"| 小皮文末通话卡 | 只在 chapter_end 文案 | 下章钩子未做成入口卡 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":