":[{"lineNumber":178,"content":"- `ajaxProxy/`：按模块拆分的请求纯函数，例如故事包、资源、调试器。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":362,"content":"## 10. 调试器静态形态要求","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":364,"content":"调试器第一版可以是静态页，但信息架构必须像运行台，而不是说明文。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/sudioV2.0版本/需求/ui/08-Studio-V2前端工程规则与质量门禁需求.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":67,"content":"- 调试器不得复刻 ExitSelector、WET 或 EffectExecutor 的业务语义。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/sudioV2.0版本/需求/ui/00-UI需求包阅读索引.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":26,"content":"7. [06-CallCard调试器界面设计导向稿.md](./06-CallCard调试器界面设计导向稿.md)  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":27,"content":"   定义调试器应如何展示一轮电话、WET、出口命中、EffectExecutor 和角色状态变化。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":56,"content":"- 用户管理页用于维护测试用户档案，服务调试器，不参与正式剧情角色建模。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":58,"content":"- 调试器展示剧情电话如何推进状态，不以 raw JSON 为主体。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":73,"content":"- 调试器时间轴回放。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":84,"content":"- 先保证调试器能讲清楚一次电话的状态推进，再展示 raw snapshot。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/sudioV2.0版本/需求/ui/01-Studio-V2-UI需求总览.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":44,"content":"### 2.3 调试器不是剧情调试器","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":46,"content":"旧调试器的问题更严重：","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":53,"content":"旧调试器更像 JSON 观察器，不像剧情运行器。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":74,"content":"- 大页面文件过长，多个页面超过 400 行，调试器页面超过 1000 行。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":132,"content":"- 调试器流程","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":162,"content":"### 4.2 CallCard 调试器","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":332,"content":"### 6.