"lineNumber":138,"content":"  shellBis/","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":139,"content":"    studio_shell_bis.ts","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":260,"content":"    summary/","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":261,"content":"    editor/","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":262,"content":"    transfer/","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":263,"content":"  debugger/","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":264,"content":"  library/","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":265,"content":"    characters/","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":266,"content":"    assets/","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":330,"content":"禁止：","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":331,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":332,"content":"```text","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":333,"content":"src/pageComponents/debugger/CallRunPanel.tsx","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":334,"content":"src/pageComponents/debugger/com/CallRunPanel.tsx","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":335,"content":"```","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":336,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":337,"content":"禁止：","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true}]}],"totalLines":33,"totalMatchedLines":6,"clientTruncated":false,"ripgrepTruncated":false}}}}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-02a3090d-5c47-4ce3-aa66-22c5ad0f24dd-34\nfc_75de3af1-faec-9ac7-ab4f-826f1ba4511d_4","startedAtMs":"1784772054838","completedAtMs":"1784772055096"},"model_call_id":"6b82946c-3426-4b1a-b96b-c24e3ae27360-7-5iad","session_id":"a37c5f81-7a23-47f7-8628-a8c00d676a4f","timestamp_ms":1784772055063}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-02a3090d-5c47-4ce3-aa66-22c5ad0f24dd-35\nfc_75de3af1-faec-9ac7-ab4f-826f1ba4511d_5","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/04-调试器界面需求.md","limit":100},"result":{"success":{"content":"# 04. 调试器界面需求\n\n路由：`/debugger`。浏览器只展示与发意图；模拟推进、可选文本 LLM 均在 **server**。\n\n相关：[02](./02-运行时协议.md) · [10](./10-用户与存档.md) · [19](../技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md) · [18](../技术设计文档/18-部署拓扑与BS架构.md) · [50](./50-对话与模型适配.md)\n\n## 1. 进入流程（用户门禁）\n\n```text\n进入 /debugger\n  → UserGate（全页或 Dialog：列表 / 新增 / 选择 / 删除；无密码）\n  → 选定 userId → 加载 PlayerProfile\n  → 进入调试台\n```\n\n与故事列表共用同一 `UserGate` 组件（见 [03](./03-编辑器界面需求.md)、[19](../技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)）。\n\n## 2. 信息架构\n\n```text\n┌──────────────┬─────────────────────────────┬──────────────────┐\n│ 模拟控制      │     Board / 时间线            │ 当前卡详情        │\n│ · 当前用户    │  各角色 pending / active      │ · Composer 快照   │\n│ · 起始卡      │  出口命中 / Free 管线         │ · 命中 promptScenes│\n│ · 本地时间覆盖│  effect / Profile diff         │ · 工具策略        │\n│ · 电话事件    │  log 切片                     │ · 出口+命中原因   │\n│ · Outcome    │                               │ · 记忆摘要        │\n│ · 时钟快进    │                               │                  │\n├──────────────┴─────────────────────────────┴──────────────────┤\n│ 底部：WET / Facts&knowledge / Lore / 校验警告 / 错误码提示        │\n└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n## 3. 基础流程\n\n```text\n选定 User → 加载 Profile（可重置）\n  → 选起始卡 → simulate_start（读已保存 Content，冻结 frozenCard）\n  → 模拟电话事件 / 文本聊 / 手动 beats·flags\n  → Story：ExitSelector → Effects\n    Free：FreeCallPostPipeline（MemoryCommit；有候选则 ExitSelector）\n  → save Profile；查看 diff 与 logs\n  → 可选快进触发 schedule（触发点 = clock + minMs）\n```\n\n对话：v1 **Manual**；可接 **server 文本 LLM** 聊天 UI（`POST /api/debug/chat` **SSE** 推送一轮事件；可保留 `refreshStamp` 兜底重拉 snapshot）。Outcome：默认 Manual；高级区可「模型建议 Outcome」再确认（见 [19 §13](../技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)）。\n\n**本地时间 / 场景组装：**\n\n- `beginCall` 上报浏览器本地时间（或「固定本地时间」覆盖）→ `ComposeScene`  \n- Composer 快照须显示：`callDirection`、本地时段 bucket、**matchedLayerIds**、最终 opening  \n- 详见 [50](./50-对话与模型适配.md)\n\n**过程话术模拟：** 按钮触发 `silence_timeout` / `call_duration_threshold` / `pre_hangup_hint`（引擎不计时）。\n\n## 4. 与编辑器严格分离\n\n- 调试器**不提供**改卡 / 改 package 的编辑 UI。\n- 本通使用 `CallSession.frozenCard`；画布未保存草稿不影响本通。\n- 发现问题：结束调试 → 回 `/stories/[id]` 修改并保存 → 再进调试。\n\n## 5. 必须显示\n\n- Profile.Board diff；命中出口原因（static / dynamic）或 Free 管线步骤\n- effect plan：`ok | skipped | failed` + plan.status\n- RuntimeExitCandidate（可手动登记模拟 FC）\n- world.facts / knowledge / memory 摘要；Lore 状态\n- Composer 快照（受显示等级约束）；**命中的 promptScenes layer**\n- **日志时间线**（Host ring + 可打开 jsonl 切片）\n- 当前 `composeScene.localTime`（可覆盖）\n\n## 5.1 调试显示等级（隐私）\n\n| 模式 | privateBrief |\n|------|----------------|\n| **author** | 可见 |\n| **playtest** | 默认隐藏；可临时揭示 |\n| **导出日志** | **不落** private 原文 |\n\n## 6. 电话事件与 Outcome\n\n接通结束、未接、占线、提前挂断、播放完成/跳过、重播、留言已听、回拨触发。预填 flags 后可改 beats，再结束通话。\n\n## 7. 非目标\n\n- 调试器内改卡或热重载本通 frozenCard\n- v1 强制 Realtime / 自动 Outcome\n- 旧话机进程连接、完整时间旅行（P1）\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":89,"fileSize":4560,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/04-调试器界面需求.md","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":89},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-02a3090d-5c47-4ce3-aa66-22c5ad0f24dd-35\nfc_75de3af1-faec-9ac7-ab4f-826f1ba4511d_5","startedAtMs":"1784772054867","completedAtMs":"1784772055102"},"model_call_id":"6b82946c-3426-4b1a-b96b-c24e3ae27360-7-5iad","session_id":"a37c5f81-7a23-47f7-8628-a8c00d676a4f","timestamp_ms":1784772055065}
