{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-0cca7537-2af6-4d3d-88a1-5680fa30d8a4-41\nfc_d4bcd9cb-7850-93c6-a645-5c55195c1180_5","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI/studio-v2/07-已知边界与下一步候选.md"},"result":{"success":{"content":"# 已知边界与下一步候选（代码事实）\n\n> 固化：2026-07-23（V2-S8-18：保存 validate 闸门 + card 级错误定位）。  \n> 「站稳」指：角色/玩家/故事包列表/编辑器读写+编辑接线+保存校验均可磁盘真源；**不等于** Host 闭环。\n\n## 1. 故意未做 / 尚未做\n\n| 项 | 现状 | 勿误判 |\n|----|------|--------|\n| 角色落盘 | **已做**：`data/characters` ↔ `/api/characters` | 勿再写「仅 MOCK_CHARACTERS」 |\n| 玩家落盘 | **已做**：`data/users` ↔ `/api/users` | 勿再写「仅 MOCK_USER_PROFILES」 |\n| 故事包 BFF + UI | **已做**：列表扫盘；编辑器打开/整包保存；`CanvasMockGraph` 已删 | 勿再写「打开仍走内存种子」 |\n| 编辑接线落盘 | **已做**：浮窗/出口/Effect/归属经整包保存写 cards+layout | 不等于 Host 真跑 Effect |\n| 保存 validate | **已做**：PUT 写后 `validatePackage`；error 回滚阻断；条幅定位到 card | warning 默认不阻断；exit 级仅 path 展示 |\n| 资源库落盘 | **已做**：`data/assets` ↔ `/api/assets`（细化修改 8） | 勿再写 MOCK_ASSETS 业务真源 |\n| Host 跑通第一幕 | 无 | 出口/Effect 仍是编辑器写 Content |\n| 调试器真会话 | 仍 mock / 可选 S8-19 仅读盘展示 validate | 本步不 Host beginCall |\n| 正式稿逐句剧本 | speakable 压缩 | 不是完整剧本导入器 |\n| 小皮文末通话卡 | 只在 chapter_end 文案 | 下章钩子未做成入口卡 |\n| 音色枚举补全 | 部分磁盘 voiceId 不在枚举 | 与 MBTI 无关的债 |\n| `pkg_memory_bar_1` | 仅调试器/设置/部分测试夹具 | 正式包 id = `wrong_number_act1` |\n\n## 2. 已站稳、可依赖的能力\n\n- 单选开属性浮窗；框选不开。  \n- CallCard / 章节属性 Formik；出口列表 + 分 effect 面板（`ExitEffectsList`）；ExitCondition v1 写 `exit.condition`。  \n- attach 效果边与 effects 行同步；保存后刷新仍在。  \n- 角色库 / 画布角色弹窗：人设 + **MBTI Select**；读写经 `/api/characters`；全库锚点。  \n- 玩家配置页：列表/新建/详情/删除经 `/api/users`。  \n- 故事包：`GET/PUT /api/stories`；PUT 经 `writeValidatedDiskStoryPackage`。  \n- 引擎：`personalityCode` → Composer systemHard（有单测）；路径 B 引用角色校验。  \n\n## 3. 下一步候选\n\n细化修改 8（S8-1–18）已收口；可选 S8-19 调试器读盘展示 validate。\n\n后置项（勿自动开干）：\n\n1. 调试器真会话 / Host 闭环  \n2. runtime/compose 目录聚类（消 STRUCT-009）  \n3. 第二幕内容包  \n4. validate 定位增强（exit 行高亮、包级 conf 浮窗跳转）\n\n## 4. 改代码前必读\n\n1. [00-Studio-V2代码事实索引](../00-Studio-V2代码事实索引.md)  \n2. [06-过程岔子与纠正记录](./06-过程岔子与纠正记录.md)  \n3. 若再动真源域 → 对照 [第三步需求](../../AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/第三步需求.md) §2.0 零残余  \n4. 动完若改变「代码事实」→ **回写本目录**\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":50,"fileSize":3013,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI/studio-v2/07-已知边界与下一步候选.md","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":50},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-0cca7537-2af6-4d3d-88a1-5680fa30d8a4-41\nfc_d4bcd9cb-7850-93c6-a645-5c55195c1180_5","startedAtMs":"1784772062067","completedAtMs":"1784772063040"},"model_call_id":"6b82946c-3426-4b1a-b96b-c24e3ae27360-8-2qwc","session_id":"a37c5f81-7a23-47f7-8628-a8c00d676a4f","timestamp_ms":1784772063084}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-0cca7537-2af6-4d3d-88a1-5680fa30d8a4-36\nfc_d4bcd9cb-7850-93c6-a645-5c55195c1180_0","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/bis/pageBis/packages/list/listStoryPackages_bis.ts"},"result":{"success":{"content":"/**\n\t* 故事包列表真源：GET /api/stories → data/storis-packages。\n\t*/\nimport { diskSummaryToPackageSummary } from \"@studio-v2/src/bis/pageBis/packages/diskSummaryMapper\";\nimport { fetchDiskStoryPackages } from \"@studio-v2/src/utils/ajaxProxy/packages/api/storiesApi\";\nimport type { StoryPackageSummary } from \"@studio-v2/typeFiles/story/summary/storyPackageSummary\";\n\n/** 磁盘扫描并投影为工作台/列表摘要 */\nexport async function listStoryPackagesFromDisk(): Promise<\n\tStoryPackageSummary[]\n> {\n\tconst disk = await fetchDiskStoryPackages();\n\treturn disk.map(diskSummaryToPackageSummary);\n}\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":15,"fileSize":614,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/bis/pageBis/packages/list/listStoryPackages_bis.ts","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":15},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-0cca7537-2af6-4d3d-88a1-5680fa30d8a4-36\nfc_d4bcd9cb-7850-93c6-a645-5c55195c1180_0","startedAtMs":"1784772062053","completedAtMs":"1784772063041"},"model_call_id":"6b82946c-3426-4b1a-b96b-c24e3ae27360-8-2qwc","session_id":"a37c5f81-7a23-47f7-8628-a8c00d676a4f","timestamp_ms":1784772063086}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-0cca7537-2af6-4d3d-88a1-5680fa30d8a4-37\nfc_d4bcd9cb-7850-93c6-a645-5c55195c1180_1","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/utils/ajaxHelper/studioApiClient.ts","limit":80},"result":{"success":{"content":"/**\n\t* Studio V2 客户端 API 响应解析（ajaxHelper）。\n\t* 统一 { ok:true, data } / { ok:false, code, message, details? }；禁止页面裸拼错误分支。\n\t*/\n\nexport type StudioApiFail = {\n\tok: false;\n\tcode: string;\n\tmessage: string;\n\tdetails?: unknown;\n};\n\nexport type StudioApiOk<T> = {\n\tok: true;\n\tdata: T;\n};\n\nexport type StudioApiEnvelope<T> = StudioApiOk<T> | StudioApiFail;\n\n/** 带 code/details 的 API 失败；保存 validate 等需读 details.report */\nexport class StudioApiError extends Error {\n\treadonly code: string;\n\treadonly details: unknown | undefined;\n\n\tconstructor(code: string, message: string, details?: unknown) {\n\t\tsuper(message);\n\t\tthis.name = \"StudioApiError\";\n\t\tthis.code = code;\n\t\tthis.details = details;\n\t}\n}\n\n/**\n\t* 解析 fetch Response；非 JSON 或业务失败时抛 StudioApiError / Error（message 为人话）。\n\t*/\nexport async function parseStudioApiJson<T>(\n\tres: Response,\n): Promise<T> {\n\tlet body: unknown;\n\ttry {\n\t\tbody = await res.json();\n\t} catch {\n\t\tthrow new Error(`请求失败（HTTP ${res.status}），响应非 JSON`);\n\t}\n\tif (\n\t\ttypeof body !== \"object\" ||\n\t\tbody === null ||\n\t\t!(\"ok\" in body)\n\t) {\n\t\tthrow new Error(`请求失败（HTTP ${res.status}），响应格式无效`);\n\t}\n\tconst envelope = body as StudioApiEnvelope<T>;\n\tif (envelope.ok === true) {\n\t\treturn envelope.data;\n\t}\n\tconst message =\n\t\ttypeof envelope.message === \"string\" && envelope.message.trim() !== \"\"\n\t\t\t? envelope.message\n\t\t\t: `请求失败（${envelope.code ?? res.status}）`;\n\tthrow new StudioApiError(\n\t\ttypeof envelope.code === \"string\" ? envelope.code : \"ENGINE_INTERNAL\",\n\t\tmessage,\n\t\tenvelope.details,\n\t);\n}\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":66,"fileSize":1660,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/utils/ajaxHelper/studioApiClient.ts","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":66},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-0cca7537-2af6-4d3d-88a1-5680fa30d8a4-37\nfc_d4bcd9cb-7850-93c6-a645-5c55195c1180_1","startedAtMs":"1784772062056","completedAtMs":"1784772063042"},"model_call_id":"6b82946c-3426-4b1a-b96b-c24e3ae27360-8-2qwc","session_id":"a37c5f81-7a23-47f7-8628-a8c00d676a4f","timestamp_ms":1784772063086}
